::Feline::

She smiled and let out a small, choked up, nervous laugh.  She felt a 
tear roll down her cheek as she looked into Chordate's eyes.
"I love it here." She pulled her hands free from his and wrapped her 
arms around him in a gratefull embrace. "Thank you." she whispered 
into his ear and she hugged him.
